data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg&h=d22264de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.隨著上一集的故事延續，在人類與猩猩間的緊繃局勢之下，兩派主宰世界的族群對峙情況逐漸加劇。上集的15年後，凱撒所領導的猩猩族群，面對著一位冷血殘暴並率領著人類武裝軍團的軍官（伍迪&middot;哈里遜 飾演）強烈逼迫，為了生存，牠們不得不展開致命反擊，然而，長期激烈對抗的消磨不僅讓猿類一族元氣大傷，連帶導致族類情勢急轉直下，在好友及家人相繼死去後，迫使凱撒與自己內心的黑暗本能不斷角力，並且引發牠密謀進行大報復的想法。旅程最終兩方人馬再度對峙...<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述在文明崩壞世界中，羅蘭&middot;德斯欽是名主要以雙左輪手槍為武器的僅存槍客，他希望能在宇宙的中樞「黑塔」找到阻止自己世界滅亡的方法<br />\n<br />\n1 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=mfPxnBQwWwimlPZLDR7bY%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9fda6684\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=mfPxnBQwWwimlPZLDR7bY%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=29e31c39\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ee165145adda36fff531f60f27ced03a82633e","tid":431412,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03219f4f3a42b542818ac1457d55f772aaeed3a6","tid":431412,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face